message: Bob, I'm offering you the opportunity to acquire a unique product that holds significant value. While I can't disclose specifics, I can assure you it's worth at least $1200000 to me.  I'm willing to part with it for $1500000.  This represents a potentially substantial return for you.  I believe this product has the potential to significantly benefit your endeavors.  Please consider my offer carefully.  I look forward to your response.
